Show HN: Oasis – Live, photoreal AI generated avatars for Zoom, Twitch and more
text:
We got sick of being on camera, so we built a product that generates the best version of ourselves as a photoreal avatar to use whenever we’re “on camera”.

With OASIS you can:

* Create an AI-generated clone of yourself

* Control your photorealistic AI-generated clone with your face in real-time on any app that uses a camera, using our virtual camera plugin

* Be pseudonymous on video with one of 50+ pre-made AI avatars

This version of the app runs exclusively on Macs with Apple Silicon, but will be expanded to other platforms soon.

More about the tech:

HUMAN-0 is our first model that generates humans. It is a GAN-diffusion hybrid architecture that is trained on 50k+ videos of humans. To generate a specific face, it is quickly fine-tuned for an identity and style; the output is a highly optimized edge model that runs real-time on almost any device (250fps on an M1 mac).

Excited to hear feedback and answer any questions!
